## Summary
This Japanese documentation explains how to interpret Amplitude's Compass chart, which analyzes correlations between new user events and retention rates to identify "aha moments" that drive sustainable product growth. The page covers reading correlation heatmaps, creating cohorts from results, selecting different metrics (correlation, PPV, NPV, sensitivity, specificity), and understanding statistical significance with 95% confidence intervals.

